title: Art Collab/Trades!
body:
Hey y'all!

I’ve been thinking, I miss getting to really collab/work with others, and been wanting to remedy that, so I’d thought I’d put the idea of collaborating on something out there! Not sure in what exact way, (probably an art piece of maybe animation!) but if anyone would like to collab, we could talk about it!

I’d also love to connect to with fellow art buds by doing some art trades for any interested!

I’m really wanting to make sure I get back into being more “involved” in the art community, as I feel like I used to be! Plus, it’s a good way to keep myself busy art-wise, which will help me personally as well!

Merry Christmas Eve Eve!
